{"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","anchor":"Essentials","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Integrate OUDS","anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Use Swift Package Manager","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"package dependency","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","type":"reference"},{"text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0-rc3","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Import the librairies you need","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" products.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Tip","type":"aside"},{"code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","type":"heading"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","type":"aside"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Import the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" product which suits your needs:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Umbrella","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUI","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"level":3,"text":"Chose your theme","anchor":"Chose-your-theme","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" framework provides today four themes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sosh","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Wireframe","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"level":3,"text":"Apply a theme","anchor":"Apply-a-theme","type":"heading"},{"numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}]}],"size":1},{"content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"size":1}],"type":"row"},{"numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}]}],"size":1},{"content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing"}],"size":1}],"type":"row"},{"style":"tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Tip","type":"aside"},{"level":3,"text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you use Xcode ","type":"text"},{"code":"#Preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit ","type":"text"},{"code":"#Preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"inside the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"title":"Getting Started with OUDS","roleHeading":"Article","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"}]},"references":{"ic_unified_ds.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_unified_ds.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Components":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/components","abstract":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components","type":"text"}]},{"text":" are the ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" objects you can add in the views of your apps, like buttons, links, cards etc."}],"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_component_intro.png"},{"identifier":"ic_component_intro.png","type":"card"}],"title":"Components","type":"topic","role":"article","kind":"article"},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/ouds/oudsthemeableview/":{"type":"link","title":"OUDSThemeableView","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","titleInlineContent":[{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"}]},"ic_module_intro.png":{"type":